          class="headshot"
          src="/images/colour-headshot-500x500.jpg"
          alt="Headshot of Nick Taylor"
          loading="lazy"
        /><p></p><p>
          Hi! My name is Nick Taylor.I am a Microsoft MVP, GitHub Star, Software
          Developer, and Developer Advocate. With over two decades in technology
          and a decade of open source contributions, plus five years of
          professional open source work at companies like <a
            href="https://opensauced.pizza">OpenSauced</a
          >, <a href="https://dev.to">dev.to</a>, and <a
            href="https://www.netlify.com/">Netlify</a
